This might be
the busiest week of your life.

00:08:39.218 --> 00:08:40.720 line:95%,end
CHRISTI: <i>Abby bit off more</i>
<i>than she could chew last week</i>

00:08:40.786 --> 00:08:43.289 line:95%,end
with trios and solos
and group dances,

00:08:43.356 --> 00:08:45.491 line:95%,end
and this week we're doing
group dances and solos

00:08:45.558 --> 00:08:47.193 line:95%,end
and the Joffrey audition.

00:08:47.260 --> 00:08:49.028 line:95%,end
Can't we just focus on one thing?

00:08:49.095 --> 00:08:50.563 line:95%,end
ABBY: I know that
I'm putting the pressure on you.

00:08:50.630 --> 00:08:51.697 line:95%,end
But you know what?

00:08:51.764 --> 00:08:53.833 line:95%,end
There's a time for pressure
and it's right now.

00:08:54.233 --> 00:08:56.469 line:95%,end
You are representing
the Abby Lee Dance Company.

00:08:56.536 --> 00:08:59.138 line:95%,end
You are representing
32 years of history.

00:08:59.205 --> 00:09:00.840 line:95%,end
Do you understand that?

00:09:00.907 --> 00:09:02.108 line:95%,end
Don't blow it.

00:09:02.441 --> 00:09:05.244 line:5%,start
(quirky music playing)

00:09:07.313 --> 00:09:08.347 line:95%,end
CATHY: <i>Girls, come on in.</i>

00:09:08.414 --> 00:09:10.917 line:95%,end
I have a really
spectacular announcement

00:09:10.983 --> 00:09:11.884 line:95%,end
that I want to make.

