00:59:37.240 --> 00:59:38.374 line:95%,end
<i>she's running home.</i>

00:59:38.441 --> 00:59:41.678 line:95%,end
<i>I think it's ridiculous you're leaving</i>
<i>because you're embarrassed</i>

00:59:41.744 --> 00:59:43.346 line:95%,end
